question: What are the top 5 movies with a runtime greater than 120 minutes?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.runtime > 120
RETURN m.title, m.runtime
ORDER BY m.runtime DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has runtime $r; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "runtime": $r };

question: List the first 3 directors born before 1950.
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director)
WHERE d.born < date('1950-01-01')
RETURN d.name, d.born
ORDER BY d.born
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: Which 5 movies have the most number of votes on IMDb?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.imdbVotes
ORDER BY m.imdbVotes DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has imdb_votes $v; sort $v desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "votes": $v };

question: Which 3 movies feature both English and Japanese languages?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE 'English' IN m.languages AND 'Japanese' IN m.languages
RETURN m.title
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: What are the top 3 movies by revenue released in 2014?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.year = 2014 AND m.revenue IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title, m.revenue
ORDER BY m.revenue DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: Which actors have played in a movie and also directed a movie?
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Who are the 5 most frequent actors in the 'Adventure' genre?
cypher:
MATCH (a:Actor)-[:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre {name: 'Adventure'})
WITH a, count(*) AS count
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 5
RETURN a.name AS actor, count
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: List the 3 oldest directors based on their birth date.
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director)
WHERE d.born IS NOT NULL
RETURN d.name, d.born
ORDER BY d.born
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: Which movies have both high revenue (over 500 million USD) and high imdbRating (above 8.0)?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.revenue > 500000000 AND m.imdbRating > 8.0
RETURN m.title, m.revenue, m.imdbRating
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has imdb_rating $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: What are the most recent 3 movies directed by any director born in Canada?
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director {bornIn: 'Canada'})-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.year
ORDER BY m.year DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Which 3 users have rated the most movies?
cypher:
MATCH (u:User)-[r:RATED]->(m:Movie)
WITH u, count(r) AS numRatings
ORDER BY numRatings DESC
LIMIT 3
RETURN u.name AS user, numRatings
typeql: match $u isa user, has name $un; $m isa movie, has title $t; (user: $u, film: $m) isa rated, has rating $r; limit 5; fetch { "user": $un, "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: What are the top 3 highest budget movies that failed to gross more than their budget?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.revenue < m.budget
RETURN m.title, m.budget, m.revenue
ORDER BY m.budget DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: Which movies have been rated by more than 1000 users?

question: What movies had a budget greater than 100 million dollars and were directed by a director born in the USA?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.budget > 100000000
AND exists {
  (d:Director)-[:DIRECTED]->(m)
  WHERE d.bornIn CONTAINS 'USA'
}
RETURN m.title, m.budget, m.year

question: What genres have more than ten movies associated with them?
cypher:
MATCH (g:Genre)<-[:IN_GENRE]-(m:Movie)
WITH g, count(m) AS movieCount
WHERE movieCount > 10
RETURN g.name AS genre, movieCount

question: Which movies have been rated by both user '1' and user '2'?

typeql: match $u isa user, has name $un; $m isa movie, has title $t; (user: $u, film: $m) isa rated, has rating $r; limit 5; fetch { "user": $un, "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: Show the top 5 genres of movies that have a runtime of exactly 90 minutes.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre)
WHERE m.runtime = 90
RETURN g.name AS genre, count(*) AS count
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (film: $m, genre: $g) isa in_genre; $g has name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: Which 3 movies have been rated by the oldest users in terms of account creation date?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[r:RATED]-(u:User)
WITH m, u, r.timestamp AS ratedAt
ORDER BY ratedAt
RETURN m.title AS movie, m.year AS year
  ORDER BY ratedAt
  LIMIT 3
typeql: match $u isa user, has name $un; $m isa movie, has title $t; (user: $u, film: $m) isa rated, has rating $r; limit 5; fetch { "user": $un, "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: What are the top 3 movies based on the number of different languages they have been released in?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, size(m.languages) AS languageCount
ORDER BY languageCount DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: Which 5 directors have the most movies released in the 2000s?
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director)-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie)
WHERE m.year >= 2000 AND m.year < 2010
WITH d, count(m) AS numMovies
ORDER BY numMovies DESC
LIMIT 5
RETURN d.name AS director, numMovies
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: What are the top 5 movies directed by directors born in Nebraska?
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director {bornIn: 'Nebraska, USA'})-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.year, m.imdbRating
ORDER BY m.imdbRating DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Which 3 movies have the lowest revenue despite having a high IMDb rating (over 7.0)?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.imdbRating > 7.0
RETURN m.title, m.revenue
ORDER BY m.revenue
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has imdb_rating $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: List the top 5 actors who have acted in movies directed by 'Anthony Stacchi'.
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director {name: 'Anthony Stacchi'})-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie)<-[:ACTED_IN]-(a:Actor)
RETURN a.name AS actor, count(*) AS appearances
ORDER BY appearances DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: What are the first 5 movies where the main actor has also directed the film?

question: Which 3 genres has 'Toy Story' been categorized under?

LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (film: $m, genre: $g) isa in_genre; $g has name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: Name the top 5 movies with the highest budget to revenue ratio.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.budget IS NOT NULL AND m.revenue IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title AS movie, m.budget / m.revenue AS budgetRevenueRatio
ORDER BY budgetRevenueRatio DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: Which 3 users have rated the most movies?
cypher:
MATCH (u:User)-[r:RATED]->(m:Movie)
WITH u, count(r) AS numRatings
ORDER BY numRatings DESC
LIMIT 3
RETURN u.name AS user, numRatings
typeql: match $u isa user, has name $un; $m isa movie, has title $t; (user: $u, film: $m) isa rated, has rating $r; limit 5; fetch { "user": $un, "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: What are the top 5 longest movies by runtime?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.runtime
ORDER BY m.runtime DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has runtime $r; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "runtime": $r };

question: List all genres associated with the movie 'Toy Story'.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie {title: 'Toy Story'})-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre)
RETURN g.name AS genre
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (film: $m, genre: $g) isa in_genre; $g has name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: List the first 3 directors born in the USA.
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director)
WHERE d.bornIn CONTAINS 'USA'
RETURN d.name, d.bornIn
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: Which movies released after 2010 have a budget over 100 million? Limit to 5 movies.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.released > '2010' AND m.budget > 100000000
RETURN m.title, m.released, m.budget
ORDER BY m.budget DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has budget $b; sort $b desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "budget": $b };

question: What are the top 3 genres by number of movies?

MATCH (g:Genre)<-[:IN_GENRE]-(m:Movie)
RETURN g.name AS genre, count(m) AS movieCount
ORDER BY movieCount DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (film: $m, genre: $g) isa in_genre; $g has name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: List 5 actors who have acted in more than 10 movies.
cypher:
MATCH (a:Actor)-[:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie)
WITH a, count(m) AS numMovies
WHERE numMovies > 10
RETURN a.name AS actor, numMovies
ORDER BY numMovies DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: List the first 3 directors who have also acted in movies.

question: Which movies have a revenue to budget ratio greater than 2? Limit to 5 movies.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.revenue IS NOT NULL AND m.budget IS NOT NULL AND m.revenue / m.budget > 2
RETURN m.title, m.revenue, m.budget, m.revenue / m.budget AS ratio
ORDER BY ratio DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: List the first 3 movies that have been directed by more than one director.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE exists{ (m)<-[:DIRECTED]-(:Director) }
WITH m
MATCH (m)<-[:DIRECTED]-(d:Director)
WITH m, count(d) AS directorCount
WHERE directorCount > 1
RETURN m.title AS movie
LIMIT 3

question: What are the top 5 movies with the smallest gap between release and rating date?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[r:RATED]-(u:User)
WITH m, r, u, datetime(m.released) AS releasedDate, datetime({epochSeconds: r.timestamp}) AS ratingDate
WITH m, duration.between(releasedDate, ratingDate).days AS daysBetween
ORDER BY daysBetween
LIMIT 5
RETURN m.title AS movie, daysBetween AS daysBetweenReleaseAndRating
typeql: match $u isa user, has name $un; $m isa movie, has title $t; (user: $u, film: $m) isa rated, has rating $r; limit 5; fetch { "user": $un, "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: Which 3 users have rated the same movie with different ratings?
cypher:
MATCH (u1:User)-[r1:RATED]->(m:Movie)<-[r2:RATED]-(u2:User), 
       (m)<-[r3:RATED]-(u3:User)
WHERE u1 <> u2 AND u1 <> u3 AND u2 <> u3
  AND r1.rating <> r2.rating
  AND r1.rating <> r3.rating
  AND r2.rating <> r3.rating
RETURN u1.name AS User1, r1.rating AS User1Rating,
       u2.name AS User2, r2.rating AS User2Rating,  
       u3.name AS User3, r3.rating AS User3Rating,
       m.title AS Movie
LIMIT 1
typeql: match $u isa user, has name $un; $m isa movie, has title $t; (user: $u, film: $m) isa rated, has rating $r; limit 5; fetch { "user": $un, "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

WITH d, count(distinct a) AS numActors
ORDER BY numActors DESC
LIMIT 3
RETURN d.name AS director, numActors
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Who are the directors of movies that have an IMDb rating greater than 8.0?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[:DIRECTED]-(d:Director)
WHERE m.imdbRating > 8.0
RETURN DISTINCT d.name AS director
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: List the top 5 movies where actors also served as directors.
cypher:

ORDER BY size(collect(p.name)) DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Which 3 movies have the highest revenue to budget ratio?
cypher:

WHERE m.budget IS NOT NULL AND m.revenue IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title AS movie, toFloat(m.revenue) / m.budget AS revenueToBudgetRatio
ORDER BY revenueToBudgetRatio DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: Which 3 actors have acted in both a highest and lowest grossing movie?
cypher:
MATCH (a:Actor)-[:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie)
WITH a, m
ORDER BY m.revenue DESC
WITH a, collect(m)[0] AS highestGrossingMovie, collect(m)[-1] AS lowestGrossingMovie

  AND exists{ (a)-[:ACTED_IN]->(lowestGrossingMovie) }
RETURN a.name AS actor, highestGrossingMovie.title AS highestGrossingMovie, lowestGrossingMovie.title AS lowestGrossingMovie
LIMIT 3

question: List the first 3 movies with the most diverse country production origins.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.countries IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title, m.countries, size(m.countries) AS numCountries
ORDER BY numCountries DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: What are the top 5 movies with a budget less than 10 million USD but revenue over 100 million USD?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.budget < 10000000 AND m.revenue > 100000000
RETURN m.title, m.budget, m.revenue
ORDER BY m.revenue DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: List the first 3 movies with plots containing the word 'adventure'.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.plot CONTAINS 'adventure'
RETURN m.title, m.plot
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: What are the top 5 oldest movies in the database?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.year
ORDER BY m.year
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has year $y; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "year": $y };

question: Which 3 movies have the highest budget to revenue ratio?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.budget IS NOT NULL AND m.revenue IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title, m.budget, m.revenue, toFloat(m.budget) / m.revenue AS budgetRevenueRatio
ORDER BY budgetRevenueRatio DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: List the first 3 directors who have directed both a comedy and a drama.
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director)-[:DIRECTED]->(m1:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g1:Genre {name: 'Comedy'}),
      (d)-[:DIRECTED]->(m2:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g2:Genre {name: 'Drama'})
RETURN d.name AS director
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: What are the top 5 movies with the most number of genres associated?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre)
WITH m, count(g) AS genreCount
ORDER BY genreCount DESC
LIMIT 5
RETURN m.title AS movie, genreCount AS numberOfGenres
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (film: $m, genre: $g) isa in_genre; $g has name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: List the first 3 actors who have acted in a movie without a poster link.
cypher:
MATCH (a:Actor)-[:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie)
WHERE m.poster IS NULL
RETURN a.name
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: What are the top 5 movies with the most detailed biographies of their directors?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[:DIRECTED]-(d:Director)
WHERE d.bio IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title AS movie, d.name AS director, d.bio AS bio
ORDER BY size(d.bio) DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Name genres in which Harold Lloyd has directed movies.
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director {name: 'Harold Lloyd'})-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre)

typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: List the first 3 movies that have been directed by actors.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie)<-[:DIRECTED]-(p)
RETURN m.title
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: What are the top 5 directors who have directed the most movies with a runtime under 90 minutes?
cypher:
MATCH (d:Director)-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie)
WHERE m.runtime < 90
WITH d, count(m) AS numMovies
ORDER BY numMovies DESC
LIMIT 5
RETURN d.name AS director, numMovies
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Which 3 actors have a bio longer than 1000 characters and have acted in more than 5 movies?
cypher:
MATCH (a:Actor)-[:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie)
WHERE size(a.bio) > 1000
WITH a, count(m) AS numMovies
WHERE numMovies > 5
RETURN a.name, a.bio, numMovies
ORDER BY numMovies DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (actor: $p, film: $m) isa acted_in; limit 5; fetch { "actor": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: List the first 3 genres with movies having an average IMDb rating under 5.
cypher:
MATCH (g:Genre)<-[:IN_GENRE]-(m:Movie)
WHERE m.imdbRating IS NOT NULL
WITH g, avg(m.imdbRating) AS avgRating
WHERE avgRating < 5
RETURN g.name AS genre, avgRating
ORDER BY avgRating
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (film: $m, genre: $g) isa in_genre; $g has name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: Which users have rated movies directed by directors born after 1960?

typeql: match $p isa person, has name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (director: $p, film: $m) isa directed; limit 5; fetch { "director": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: What are the 3 most common countries for movie settings in the database?

LIMIT 3
